    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good, reliable condition and has been well-cared for during its time on the road. The exterior looks great overall, though you will find some minor stone chips and light surface scratches consistent with regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, with only slight wear on the driver's seat bolster and common touchpoints. Mechanically, it performs well, with a smooth engine and transmission, and it has a documented service history. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that is ready for its next owner to drive and enjoy immediately.",
