      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, presented in showroom condition. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with zero rock chips or swirl marks, protected by a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the premium leather remains supple and retains its original scent, with no visible wear on the seat bolsters or touchpoints. Every electronic feature and mechanical component functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and serviced exclusively by the dealership, this car comes with a complete paper trail of its history. For the collector or enthusiast who demands perfection, this is the finest example available on the market today.",
      "price": 48900.0,
